{"tid":524481,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"旗艦規格入門售價 下一代iPhone SE將支援無線充電","createTime":"2018-01-09T15:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T11:55:44.000Z","uid":13663,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"78aeaeef270089bc926c5cce1118d3c66165c6fd","tid":524481,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T15:22:05.000Z","msg":"在蘋果公司（Apple）的旗艦智慧型手機iPhone X不斷引爆市場討論度之下，蘋果下一代中階手機iPhone SE的設計也備受矚目。根據外媒報導，蘋果可能將原先旗艦機種的「無線充電」功能下放至中低階機種的iPhone SE身上。<br />\n<br />\n在蘋果的產品策略中，除了iPhone X、iPhone 8等配備頂級售價也昂貴的旗艦級智慧型手機之外，還有提供給預算有限用戶的較低價選擇，就是定位為入門級手機的iPhone SE。而根據外媒Tekz24報導，目前披露的下一代iPhone SE設計上將採用同iPhone X的玻璃背蓋，並可能支援無線充電功能。該報導也指出，下一代iPhone SE可能內建四核心A10處理器，以2GB記憶體搭配32或128GB的儲存空間，螢幕尺寸則在4至4.2吋之間。<br />\n<br />\n依據市場調查研究機構TrendForce的說法，為了滿足各階層的市場需求，蘋果可能會為了中階市場，在2018年第2季推出第2代的iPhone SE系列。此外，外媒MacRumors也認為iPhone SE將在2018年的上半年出現，並指出這批訂單可能由緯創在印度的工廠區製造。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819a5fd7de146dcdb0493741c3c316657db92d11","tid":524481,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"冇可能a10,se 都a9啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c5eaa300baf5bd8c20d98d916ac99a679cd4d2","tid":524481,"uid":4284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"819a5fd7de146dcdb0493741c3c316657db92d11","tid":524481,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"冇可能a10,se 都a9啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T15:35:24.000Z","msg":"係a11就正，不過難啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7b95e3c83c526f4619eacb2a21417b19108755","tid":524481,"uid":16756,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"819a5fd7de146dcdb0493741c3c316657db92d11